TextMate Bundle for writing YARD style documentation for ruby scripts

Snippets:
  @par - @params
  @si  - @since
  @ver - @version
  @au  - @author
  @see - @see
  @rai - @rai
  @ypar - @yieldparam
  @y   - @yield
  @ret - @return
  @dep - @deprecated

